[
  {
    "startTime": 14222,
    "endTime": 16888,
    "duration": 2666,
    "text": "OK, first, some introductions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17919,
    "endTime": 20142,
    "duration": 2223,
    "text": "My mom, Jennie, took this picture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21158,
    "endTime": 23497,
    "duration": 2339,
    "text": "That's my dad, Frank, in the middle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24139,
    "endTime": 26283,
    "duration": 2144,
    "text": "And on his left, my sisters:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26766,
    "endTime": 30791,
    "duration": 4025,
    "text": "Mary Catherine, Judith Ann,\nTheresa Marie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30815,
    "endTime": 34739,
    "duration": 3924,
    "text": "John Patrick's sitting on his lap\nand Kevin Michael's on his right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35739,
    "endTime": 38212,
    "duration": 2473,
    "text": "And in the pale-blue windbreaker,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38236,
    "endTime": 40381,
    "duration": 2145,
    "text": "Susan Diane. Me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41491,
    "endTime": 44619,
    "duration": 3128,
    "text": "I loved growing up in a big family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45159,
    "endTime": 48832,
    "duration": 3673,
    "text": "And one of my favorite things\nwas picking names."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49924,
    "endTime": 53369,
    "duration": 3445,
    "text": "But by the time child\nnumber seven came along,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53393,
    "endTime": 55710,
    "duration": 2317,
    "text": "we had nearly run out of middle names."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57075,
    "endTime": 58917,
    "duration": 1842,
    "text": "It was a long deliberation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58941,
    "endTime": 62948,
    "duration": 4007,
    "text": "before we finally settled\non Jennifer Bridget."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64353,
    "endTime": 67084,
    "duration": 2731,
    "text": "Every parent in this audience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67108,
    "endTime": 69732,
    "duration": 2624,
    "text": "knows the joy and excitement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69756,
    "endTime": 72194,
    "duration": 2438,
    "text": "of picking a new baby's name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72913,
    "endTime": 74835,
    "duration": 1922,
    "text": "And I was excited and thrilled"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74859,
    "endTime": 78562,
    "duration": 3703,
    "text": "to help my mom in that special\nceremonial moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79824,
    "endTime": 81863,
    "duration": 2039,
    "text": "But it's not like that everywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83163,
    "endTime": 85846,
    "duration": 2683,
    "text": "I travel a lot and I see a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86273,
    "endTime": 89366,
    "duration": 3093,
    "text": "But it took me by surprise to learn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89390,
    "endTime": 91569,
    "duration": 2179,
    "text": "in an area of Ethiopia,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91593,
    "endTime": 95274,
    "duration": 3681,
    "text": "parents delay picking the names\nfor their new babies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95298,
    "endTime": 96849,
    "duration": 1551,
    "text": "by a month or more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97908,
    "endTime": 99325,
    "duration": 1417,
    "text": "Why delay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100278,
    "endTime": 103645,
    "duration": 3367,
    "text": "Why not take advantage\nof this special ceremonial time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104423,
    "endTime": 106820,
    "duration": 2397,
    "text": "Well, they delay because they're afraid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108007,
    "endTime": 110224,
    "duration": 2217,
    "text": "They're afraid their baby will die."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111080,
    "endTime": 116230,
    "duration": 5150,
    "text": "And this loss might be a little more\nbearable without a name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117248,
    "endTime": 121153,
    "duration": 3905,
    "text": "A face without a name might help them feel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121177,
    "endTime": 123946,
    "duration": 2769,
    "text": "just a little less attached."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125019,
    "endTime": 127496,
    "duration": 2477,
    "text": "So here we are in one part of the world --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127520,
    "endTime": 132261,
    "duration": 4741,
    "text": "a time of joy, excitement,\ndreaming of the future of that child --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132893,
    "endTime": 135155,
    "duration": 2262,
    "text": "while in another world,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135179,
    "endTime": 138099,
    "duration": 2920,
    "text": "parents are filled with dread,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138123,
    "endTime": 141698,
    "duration": 3575,
    "text": "not daring to dream\nof a future for their child"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141722,
    "endTime": 143588,
    "duration": 1866,
    "text": "beyond a few precious weeks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144789,
    "endTime": 146185,
    "duration": 1396,
    "text": "How can that be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147189,
    "endTime": 152674,
    "duration": 5485,
    "text": "How can it be that 2.6 million babies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152698,
    "endTime": 154492,
    "duration": 1794,
    "text": "die around the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154516,
    "endTime": 156936,
    "duration": 2420,
    "text": "before they're even one month old?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157926,
    "endTime": 159901,
    "duration": 1975,
    "text": "2.6 million."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161034,
    "endTime": 163353,
    "duration": 2319,
    "text": "That's the population of Vancouver."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164512,
    "endTime": 166631,
    "duration": 2119,
    "text": "And the shocking thing is:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167043,
    "endTime": 168341,
    "duration": 1298,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168365,
    "endTime": 172135,
    "duration": 3770,
    "text": "In too many cases, we simply don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173145,
    "endTime": 177271,
    "duration": 4126,
    "text": "Now, I remember recently seeing\nan updated pie chart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177295,
    "endTime": 179463,
    "duration": 2168,
    "text": "And the pie chart was labeled,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179487,
    "endTime": 182999,
    "duration": 3512,
    "text": "\"Causes of death in children\nunder five worldwide.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183838,
    "endTime": 187883,
    "duration": 4045,
    "text": "And there was a pretty big section\nof that pie chart, about 40 percent --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187907,
    "endTime": 191269,
    "duration": 3362,
    "text": "40 percent was labeled \"neonatal.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192077,
    "endTime": 194454,
    "duration": 2377,
    "text": "Now, \"neonatal\" is not a cause of death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194920,
    "endTime": 197687,
    "duration": 2767,
    "text": "Neonatal is simply an adjective,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197711,
    "endTime": 202579,
    "duration": 4868,
    "text": "an adjective that means that the child\nis less than one month old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203656,
    "endTime": 208013,
    "duration": 4357,
    "text": "For me, \"neonatal\" said:\n\"We have no idea.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209100,
    "endTime": 211270,
    "duration": 2170,
    "text": "Now, I'm a scientist. I'm a doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211294,
    "endTime": 212787,
    "duration": 1493,
    "text": "I want to fix things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213580,
    "endTime": 217445,
    "duration": 3865,
    "text": "But you can't fix\nwhat you can't define."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218227,
    "endTime": 222995,
    "duration": 4768,
    "text": "So our first step in restoring\nthe dreams of those parents"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223019,
    "endTime": 225196,
    "duration": 2177,
    "text": "is to answer the question:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225220,
    "endTime": 227169,
    "duration": 1949,
    "text": "Why are babies dying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228359,
    "endTime": 232094,
    "duration": 3735,
    "text": "So today, I want to talk\nabout a new approach,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232118,
    "endTime": 234055,
    "duration": 1937,
    "text": "an approach that I feel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234079,
    "endTime": 238763,
    "duration": 4684,
    "text": "will not only help us\nknow why babies are dying,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239367,
    "endTime": 242744,
    "duration": 3377,
    "text": "but is beginning to completely transform"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242768,
    "endTime": 244552,
    "duration": 1784,
    "text": "the whole field of global health."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246235,
    "endTime": 249361,
    "duration": 3126,
    "text": "It's called \"Precision Public Health.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250615,
    "endTime": 255615,
    "duration": 5000,
    "text": "For me, precision medicine comes\nfrom a very special place."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256894,
    "endTime": 259701,
    "duration": 2807,
    "text": "I trained as a cancer doctor,\nan oncologist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260079,
    "endTime": 263697,
    "duration": 3618,
    "text": "I got into it because I wanted\nto help people feel better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264491,
    "endTime": 268296,
    "duration": 3805,
    "text": "But too often my treatments\nmade them feel worse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269277,
    "endTime": 274013,
    "duration": 4736,
    "text": "I still remember young women\nbeing driven to my clinic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274550,
    "endTime": 275744,
    "duration": 1194,
    "text": "by their moms --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276611,
    "endTime": 281410,
    "duration": 4799,
    "text": "adults, who had to be helped\ninto my exam room by their mothers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282791,
    "endTime": 283951,
    "duration": 1160,
    "text": "They were so weak"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283975,
    "endTime": 286204,
    "duration": 2229,
    "text": "from the treatment I had given them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287283,
    "endTime": 291483,
    "duration": 4200,
    "text": "But at the time, in those front lines\nin the war on cancer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291507,
    "endTime": 293141,
    "duration": 1634,
    "text": "we had few tools."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294030,
    "endTime": 297722,
    "duration": 3692,
    "text": "And the tools we did have\ncouldn't differentiate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297746,
    "endTime": 301020,
    "duration": 3274,
    "text": "between the cancer cells\nthat we wanted to hit hard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301670,
    "endTime": 305109,
    "duration": 3439,
    "text": "and those healthy cells\nthat we wanted to preserve."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306663,
    "endTime": 309618,
    "duration": 2955,
    "text": "And so the side effects that you're\nall very familiar with --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309642,
    "endTime": 312476,
    "duration": 2834,
    "text": "hair loss, being sick to your stomach,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312500,
    "endTime": 316614,
    "duration": 4114,
    "text": "having a suppressed immune system,\nso infection was a constant threat --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317179,
    "endTime": 319964,
    "duration": 2785,
    "text": "were always surrounding us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320985,
    "endTime": 323694,
    "duration": 2709,
    "text": "And then I moved\nto the biotechnology industry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324269,
    "endTime": 328349,
    "duration": 4080,
    "text": "And I got to work on a new approach\nfor breast cancer patients"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328373,
    "endTime": 333374,
    "duration": 5001,
    "text": "that could do a better job\nof telling the healthy cells"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333398,
    "endTime": 335740,
    "duration": 2342,
    "text": "from the unhealthy or cancer cells."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336566,
    "endTime": 338589,
    "duration": 2023,
    "text": "It's a drug called Herceptin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339343,
    "endTime": 342579,
    "duration": 3236,
    "text": "And what Herceptin allowed us to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342603,
    "endTime": 347814,
    "duration": 5211,
    "text": "is to precisely target\nHER2-positive breast cancer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349036,
    "endTime": 351718,
    "duration": 2682,
    "text": "at the time, the scariest\nform of breast cancer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352091,
    "endTime": 355926,
    "duration": 3835,
    "text": "And that precision let us\nhit hard the cancer cells,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356727,
    "endTime": 360817,
    "duration": 4090,
    "text": "while sparing and being more\ngentle on the normal cells."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362441,
    "endTime": 364157,
    "duration": 1716,
    "text": "A huge breakthrough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364181,
    "endTime": 366261,
    "duration": 2080,
    "text": "It felt like a miracle,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367091,
    "endTime": 370040,
    "duration": 2949,
    "text": "so much so that today,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370064,
    "endTime": 372595,
    "duration": 2531,
    "text": "we're harnessing all those tools --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373156,
    "endTime": 378680,
    "duration": 5524,
    "text": "big data, consumer monitoring,\ngene sequencing and more --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378704,
    "endTime": 382025,
    "duration": 3321,
    "text": "to tackle a broad variety of diseases."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383044,
    "endTime": 388113,
    "duration": 5069,
    "text": "That's allowing us to target individuals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388137,
    "endTime": 391421,
    "duration": 3284,
    "text": "with the right remedies at the right time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392731,
    "endTime": 397191,
    "duration": 4460,
    "text": "Precision medicine\nrevolutionized cancer therapy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397655,
    "endTime": 399257,
    "duration": 1602,
    "text": "Everything changed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400187,
    "endTime": 403308,
    "duration": 3121,
    "text": "And I want everything to change again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404214,
    "endTime": 406466,
    "duration": 2252,
    "text": "So I've been asking myself:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406490,
    "endTime": 408308,
    "duration": 1818,
    "text": "Why should we limit"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408332,
    "endTime": 413141,
    "duration": 4809,
    "text": "this smarter, more precise,\nbetter way to tackle diseases"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413165,
    "endTime": 414328,
    "duration": 1163,
    "text": "to the rich world?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416105,
    "endTime": 417617,
    "duration": 1512,
    "text": "Now, don't misunderstand me --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417641,
    "endTime": 420967,
    "duration": 3326,
    "text": "I'm not talking about bringing\nexpensive medicines like Herceptin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420991,
    "endTime": 422876,
    "duration": 1885,
    "text": "to the developing world,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422900,
    "endTime": 425150,
    "duration": 2250,
    "text": "although I'd actually kind of like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425707,
    "endTime": 427672,
    "duration": 1965,
    "text": "What I am talking about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427696,
    "endTime": 432064,
    "duration": 4368,
    "text": "is moving from this precise\ntargeting for individuals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432088,
    "endTime": 434731,
    "duration": 2643,
    "text": "to tackle public health problems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434755,
    "endTime": 436496,
    "duration": 1741,
    "text": "in populations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438487,
    "endTime": 443070,
    "duration": 4583,
    "text": "Now, OK, I know probably\nyou're thinking, \"She's crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443094,
    "endTime": 446086,
    "duration": 2992,
    "text": "You can't do that. That's too ambitious.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446830,
    "endTime": 448332,
    "duration": 1502,
    "text": "But here's the thing:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449180,
    "endTime": 452478,
    "duration": 3298,
    "text": "we're already doing this in a limited way,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452502,
    "endTime": 455572,
    "duration": 3070,
    "text": "and it's already starting\nto make a big difference."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456606,
    "endTime": 458135,
    "duration": 1529,
    "text": "So here's what's happening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458952,
    "endTime": 461542,
    "duration": 2590,
    "text": "Now, I told you I trained\nas a cancer doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461566,
    "endTime": 466015,
    "duration": 4449,
    "text": "But like many, many doctors\nwho trained in San Francisco in the '80s,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466039,
    "endTime": 468130,
    "duration": 2091,
    "text": "I also trained as an AIDS doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469077,
    "endTime": 470685,
    "duration": 1608,
    "text": "It was a terrible time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471504,
    "endTime": 473542,
    "duration": 2038,
    "text": "AIDS was a death sentence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474385,
    "endTime": 476011,
    "duration": 1626,
    "text": "All my patients died."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477329,
    "endTime": 479233,
    "duration": 1904,
    "text": "Now, things are better,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479257,
    "endTime": 483836,
    "duration": 4579,
    "text": "but HIV/AIDS remains\na terrible global challenge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484473,
    "endTime": 489924,
    "duration": 5451,
    "text": "Worldwide, about 17 million women\nare living with HIV."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490744,
    "endTime": 494041,
    "duration": 3297,
    "text": "We know that when these women\nbecome pregnant,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494065,
    "endTime": 496678,
    "duration": 2613,
    "text": "they can transfer the virus to their baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498551,
    "endTime": 500803,
    "duration": 2252,
    "text": "We also know in the absence of therapy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500827,
    "endTime": 504310,
    "duration": 3483,
    "text": "half those babies will not survive\nuntil the age of two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505446,
    "endTime": 510583,
    "duration": 5137,
    "text": "But we know that antiretroviral therapy\ncan virtually guarantee"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510607,
    "endTime": 513558,
    "duration": 2951,
    "text": "that she will not transmit\nthe virus to the baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513860,
    "endTime": 515241,
    "duration": 1381,
    "text": "So what do we do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515708,
    "endTime": 520270,
    "duration": 4562,
    "text": "Well, a one-size-fits-all approach,\nkind of like that blast of chemo,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520294,
    "endTime": 523474,
    "duration": 3180,
    "text": "would mean we test and treat\nevery pregnant woman in the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523952,
    "endTime": 525333,
    "duration": 1381,
    "text": "That would do the job."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525889,
    "endTime": 528141,
    "duration": 2252,
    "text": "But it's just not practical."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529223,
    "endTime": 534863,
    "duration": 5640,
    "text": "So instead, we target those areas\nwhere HIV rates are the highest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535444,
    "endTime": 539821,
    "duration": 4377,
    "text": "We know in certain countries\nin sub-Saharan Africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539845,
    "endTime": 544007,
    "duration": 4162,
    "text": "we can test and treat pregnant women\nwhere rates are highest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544794,
    "endTime": 547952,
    "duration": 3158,
    "text": "This precision approach\nto a public health problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547976,
    "endTime": 550377,
    "duration": 2401,
    "text": "has cut by nearly half"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550401,
    "endTime": 553156,
    "duration": 2755,
    "text": "HIV transmission from mothers to baby"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553180,
    "endTime": 555014,
    "duration": 1834,
    "text": "in the last five years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555485,
    "endTime": 559850,
    "duration": 4365,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560945,
    "endTime": 566007,
    "duration": 5062,
    "text": "Screening pregnant women\nin certain areas in the developing world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566031,
    "endTime": 569135,
    "duration": 3104,
    "text": "is a powerful example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569159,
    "endTime": 574674,
    "duration": 5515,
    "text": "of how precision public health\ncan change things on a big scale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576452,
    "endTime": 577603,
    "duration": 1151,
    "text": "So ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578213,
    "endTime": 579390,
    "duration": 1177,
    "text": "How do we do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579414,
    "endTime": 581579,
    "duration": 2165,
    "text": "We can do that because we know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581896,
    "endTime": 584214,
    "duration": 2318,
    "text": "We know who to target,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584238,
    "endTime": 585925,
    "duration": 1687,
    "text": "what to target,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585949,
    "endTime": 588241,
    "duration": 2292,
    "text": "where to target and how to target."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588685,
    "endTime": 592987,
    "duration": 4302,
    "text": "And that, for me, are the important \nelements of precision public health:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593780,
    "endTime": 596068,
    "duration": 2288,
    "text": "who, what, where and how."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597814,
    "endTime": 601715,
    "duration": 3901,
    "text": "But let's go back\nto the 2.6 million babies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601739,
    "endTime": 603756,
    "duration": 2017,
    "text": "who die before they're one month old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603780,
    "endTime": 606040,
    "duration": 2260,
    "text": "Here's the problem: we just don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606753,
    "endTime": 609217,
    "duration": 2464,
    "text": "It may seem unbelievable,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609241,
    "endTime": 614104,
    "duration": 4863,
    "text": "but the way we figure out\nthe causes of infant mortality"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614128,
    "endTime": 617139,
    "duration": 3011,
    "text": "in those countries\nwith the highest infant mortality"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617163,
    "endTime": 619159,
    "duration": 1996,
    "text": "is a conversation with mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619948,
    "endTime": 624326,
    "duration": 4378,
    "text": "A health worker asks a mom\nwho has just lost her child,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624350,
    "endTime": 628019,
    "duration": 3669,
    "text": "\"Was the baby vomiting?\nDid they have a fever?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628043,
    "endTime": 629992,
    "duration": 1949,
    "text": "And that conversation may take place"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630016,
    "endTime": 633927,
    "duration": 3911,
    "text": "as long as three months\nafter the baby has died."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634951,
    "endTime": 638099,
    "duration": 3148,
    "text": "Now, put yourself\nin the shoes of that mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639239,
    "endTime": 643195,
    "duration": 3956,
    "text": "It's a heartbreaking,\nexcruciating conversation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643833,
    "endTime": 646762,
    "duration": 2929,
    "text": "And even worse -- it's not that helpful,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647635,
    "endTime": 650588,
    "duration": 2953,
    "text": "because we might know\nthere was a fever or vomiting,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650612,
    "endTime": 652325,
    "duration": 1713,
    "text": "but we don't know why."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653171,
    "endTime": 656653,
    "duration": 3482,
    "text": "So in the absence of knowing\nthat knowledge,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656677,
    "endTime": 659659,
    "duration": 2982,
    "text": "we cannot prevent that mom, that family,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659683,
    "endTime": 661781,
    "duration": 2098,
    "text": "or other families in that community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661805,
    "endTime": 663753,
    "duration": 1948,
    "text": "from suffering the same tragedy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664804,
    "endTime": 668278,
    "duration": 3474,
    "text": "But what if we applied\na precision public health approach?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669064,
    "endTime": 670458,
    "duration": 1394,
    "text": "Let's say, for example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 670482,
    "endTime": 673416,
    "duration": 2934,
    "text": "we find out in certain areas of Africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673440,
    "endTime": 677186,
    "duration": 3746,
    "text": "that babies are dying\nbecause of a bacterial infection"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677210,
    "endTime": 679757,
    "duration": 2547,
    "text": "transferred from the mother to the baby,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 679781,
    "endTime": 682254,
    "duration": 2473,
    "text": "known as Group B streptococcus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682999,
    "endTime": 688511,
    "duration": 5512,
    "text": "In the absence of treatment,\nmom has a seven times higher chance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688535,
    "endTime": 690735,
    "duration": 2200,
    "text": "that her next baby will die."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692124,
    "endTime": 696025,
    "duration": 3901,
    "text": "Once we define the problem,\nwe can prevent that death"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696049,
    "endTime": 700132,
    "duration": 4083,
    "text": "with something as cheap\nand safe as penicillin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 701894,
    "endTime": 704445,
    "duration": 2551,
    "text": "We can do that because then we'll know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705034,
    "endTime": 706566,
    "duration": 1532,
    "text": "And that's the point:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706590,
    "endTime": 710026,
    "duration": 3436,
    "text": "once we know, we can bring\nthe right interventions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 710050,
    "endTime": 713589,
    "duration": 3539,
    "text": "to the right population\nin the right places"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713613,
    "endTime": 715036,
    "duration": 1423,
    "text": "to save lives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716973,
    "endTime": 720725,
    "duration": 3752,
    "text": "With this approach,\nand with these interventions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720749,
    "endTime": 722774,
    "duration": 2025,
    "text": "and others like them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 722798,
    "endTime": 724509,
    "duration": 1711,
    "text": "I have no doubt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724533,
    "endTime": 727080,
    "duration": 2547,
    "text": "that a precision public health approach"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 727104,
    "endTime": 730590,
    "duration": 3486,
    "text": "can help our world achieve\nour 15-year goal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 731423,
    "endTime": 735752,
    "duration": 4329,
    "text": "And that would translate\ninto a million babies' lives saved"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735776,
    "endTime": 737413,
    "duration": 1637,
    "text": "every single year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 738253,
    "endTime": 742563,
    "duration": 4310,
    "text": "One million babies every single year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 743706,
    "endTime": 745548,
    "duration": 1842,
    "text": "And why would we stop there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 746319,
    "endTime": 749616,
    "duration": 3297,
    "text": "A much more powerful approach\nto public health --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749640,
    "endTime": 752405,
    "duration": 2765,
    "text": "imagine what might be possible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 752912,
    "endTime": 756301,
    "duration": 3389,
    "text": "Why couldn't we more effectively\ntackle malnutrition?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 757643,
    "endTime": 761920,
    "duration": 4277,
    "text": "Why wouldn't we prevent\ncervical cancer in women?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 762832,
    "endTime": 765650,
    "duration": 2818,
    "text": "And why not eradicate malaria?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765674,
    "endTime": 766675,
    "duration": 1001,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 766699,
    "endTime": 767912,
    "duration": 1213,
    "text": "Yes, clap for that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 767936,
    "endTime": 771864,
    "duration": 3928,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 771888,
    "endTime": 774731,
    "duration": 2843,
    "text": "So, you know, I live\nin two different worlds,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 774755,
    "endTime": 777963,
    "duration": 3208,
    "text": "one world populated by scientists,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 778590,
    "endTime": 782487,
    "duration": 3897,
    "text": "and another world populated\nby public health professionals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 783319,
    "endTime": 785747,
    "duration": 2428,
    "text": "The promise of precision public health"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 785771,
    "endTime": 788095,
    "duration": 2324,
    "text": "is to bring these two worlds together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 788876,
    "endTime": 792421,
    "duration": 3545,
    "text": "But you know, we all live in two worlds:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 793254,
    "endTime": 796333,
    "duration": 3079,
    "text": "the rich world and the poor world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 797760,
    "endTime": 801610,
    "duration": 3850,
    "text": "And what I'm most excited about\nabout precision public health"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 801634,
    "endTime": 804093,
    "duration": 2459,
    "text": "is bridging these two worlds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 805051,
    "endTime": 808071,
    "duration": 3020,
    "text": "Every day in the rich world,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 808095,
    "endTime": 811350,
    "duration": 3255,
    "text": "we're bringing incredible\ntalent and tools --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 811374,
    "endTime": 813333,
    "duration": 1959,
    "text": "everything at our disposal --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 813357,
    "endTime": 818270,
    "duration": 4913,
    "text": "to precisely target diseases\nin ways I never imagined"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 818294,
    "endTime": 820128,
    "duration": 1834,
    "text": "would be possible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 820152,
    "endTime": 825168,
    "duration": 5016,
    "text": "Surely, we can tap into\nthat kind of talent and tools"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 825192,
    "endTime": 827630,
    "duration": 2438,
    "text": "to stop babies dying in the poor world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 829201,
    "endTime": 831250,
    "duration": 2049,
    "text": "If we did,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 831274,
    "endTime": 835331,
    "duration": 4057,
    "text": "then every parent would have\nthe confidence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 835355,
    "endTime": 839683,
    "duration": 4328,
    "text": "to name their child\nthe moment that child is born,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840746,
    "endTime": 845931,
    "duration": 5185,
    "text": "daring to dream that that child's life\nwill be measured in decades,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846498,
    "endTime": 847742,
    "duration": 1244,
    "text": "not days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 848330,
    "endTime": 849481,
    "duration": 1151,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849505,
    "endTime": 857137,
    "duration": 7632,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]